{"tid":1420410,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於民間記者會 我有少少睇法","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:45.000Z","uid":17393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"385e717e887ca515cc22e0062e97dfcfc1dbfe15","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"民間記者會長遠係抗衡政府民宣嘅channel, 我覺得模式可以改一改:<br />\n1 交代過去發生事件中 警察濫權或濫暴的證據和質疑<br />\n2 反擊政府和某些傳媒偏頗立場和不盡不實的報導和說法 令普遍大眾了解整個事實<br />\n3 整合當日民間的不同聲明和舉辦的活動 邀請市民自行閱讀聲明和有志之士參與活動<br />\n4 答問環節如針對某個指定群組的行為和言論 可先行記錄 再從連登或其他渠道尋求答案<br />\n<br />\n記者會不是大台(x3) 不用有單一立場 只需公佈客觀事實 反擊政府<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指證 歡迎提供意見 天佑香港"},{"pid":"f566aa5095f132bcadb4843f8f9ed2ede9465fb1","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"2fb16cd947e61b932786184d2e29327480a2e19f","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"78fa5e4b5b4f58d3bd0404842654454ee2f75c65","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"402bda73af60fcb55913347a5ecb53cac6d88ff1","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f6f9623258dbb0fcdbd55d9d8c59ea3cb6c2152d","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"271720e285a447ba48f111064a0ea85074f5e9c6","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0e514c34628fb332e1c558fd01c442be6a4c39cf","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8e69e7aac50a69cabced3225ee47d60ed8b7ae19","tid":1420410,"uid":17393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:17.0